  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"The volcano is seven hundred miles square and ten thousand feet high. Foolish always thought about the volcano's fierceness and how it disturbed the people, so he decided to destroy it!\"</h2>So, the heaven was moved by Foolishes' piety and decided to send you to help Foolish destroy the volcano.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Volcano</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/77c682720841f69d6e60a813155caea2.avif?t=1735914436\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br>The mood of the volcano is uncertain, and it will erupt every once in a while. Once it erupts, Yugong will be devastated. Please help the Foolishes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/8e1ef111d62ea6b148f9c8e6de813efa.poster.avif?t=1735914436\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/8e1ef111d62ea6b148f9c8e6de813efa.webm?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/8e1ef111d62ea6b148f9c8e6de813efa.mp4?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What should I do?</strong></h2>Hey! It happens that you are the god who controls mouse clicks and cards to create Foolishes! Please help the Foolisheswith the power of the mouse and the cards that are more powerful than clay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/1617fe6ecbe93e491a8febd1cf780976.poster.avif?t=1735914436\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/1617fe6ecbe93e491a8febd1cf780976.webm?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/1617fe6ecbe93e491a8febd1cf780976.mp4?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A strategic placement game</strong></h2>During this period, God will also lend you a hand. After extinguishing each round of fire, you will<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Gain the power of new cards<br></li><li> Understand new management strategies to manage Foolish</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/b38085f5d0900534f16f9abf15454235.poster.avif?t=1735914436\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/b38085f5d0900534f16f9abf15454235.webm?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/b38085f5d0900534f16f9abf15454235.mp4?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Content</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 10-20 hours game content<br></li><li> 50+cards</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >If you like to explore various genres and playing styles in the game, this game is definitely for you. </h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"The volcano is seven hundred miles square and ten thousand feet high. Foolish always thought about the volcano's fierceness and how it disturbed the people, so he decided to destroy it!\"</h2>So, the heaven was moved by Foolishes' piety and decided to send you to help Foolish destroy the volcano.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Volcano</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/77c682720841f69d6e60a813155caea2.avif?t=1735914436\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br>The mood of the volcano is uncertain, and it will erupt every once in a while. Once it erupts, Yugong will be devastated. Please help the Foolishes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/8e1ef111d62ea6b148f9c8e6de813efa.poster.avif?t=1735914436\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/8e1ef111d62ea6b148f9c8e6de813efa.webm?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/8e1ef111d62ea6b148f9c8e6de813efa.mp4?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What should I do?</strong></h2>Hey! It happens that you are the god who controls mouse clicks and cards to create Foolishes! Please help the Foolisheswith the power of the mouse and the cards that are more powerful than clay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/1617fe6ecbe93e491a8febd1cf780976.poster.avif?t=1735914436\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/1617fe6ecbe93e491a8febd1cf780976.webm?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/1617fe6ecbe93e491a8febd1cf780976.mp4?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A strategic placement game</strong></h2>During this period, God will also lend you a hand. After extinguishing each round of fire, you will<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Gain the power of new cards<br></li><li> Understand new management strategies to manage Foolish</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/b38085f5d0900534f16f9abf15454235.poster.avif?t=1735914436\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/b38085f5d0900534f16f9abf15454235.webm?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164730/extras/b38085f5d0900534f16f9abf15454235.mp4?t=1735914436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Content</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 10-20 hours game content<br></li><li> 50+cards</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >If you like to explore various genres and playing styles in the game, this game is definitely for you. </h2>",
